1. e4 e5 2. f4 { The King's Gambit! } 2... exf4 { This is the King's Gambit Accepted. The immediate threat right now from black is Qh4+, and white's in a bit of trouble because the poor king will be forced to bongcloud to e2. So to avoid any trouble, white can stop black's queen from going to h4 with 3. Nf3! 3. Bc4 is also a popular option, but it's brings white quite a few complications. } { [%csl Rh4] } 3. Nf3! { The knight is now controlling the important h4 square. } { [%csl Gh4][%cal Gf3h4] } *


[Event "King's Gambit | Full Repertoire: KGA: Fischer Defense 3...d6"]
