{ We’ve got all our pieces aiming at the king, but how can we break through Black's fortress? } { [%csl Gg6,Gg2,Ge6,Gb2] }
1. Rxh6+!! gxh6 { If Kxh6 there's also a very beautiful checkmate with 2. Qg5+ Kh7 3. Qh4+ Kg6 4. f5# } { [%csl Ge6,Gg2,Gb2] } (1... Kxh6 2. Qg5+ Kh7 3. Qh4+ Kg6 4. f5#) 2. Qg8+!! { Yes! An empty square sacrifice! We force Black to place the knight on g8, taking away a crucial escape square from the king. } { [%cal Rh7g8] } 2... Nxg8 { And now the final blow! } { [%csl Rg8,Rh6] } 3. Bf5# { [%csl Yh7,Bh8,Bg7,Rh6,Rg8][%cal Yf5h7,Bb2h8] } *


