1. Qg4+!! { Yes! The first correct move of the sequence! We're traping the Black king among his own pieces. } { [%csl Rg4,Rh4,Rh6] } 1... Bxg4 $7 2. Rxh6+!! gxh6 $7 { Now for the final move... } { [%csl Rh6,Rh5,Rh4,Rg4,Bg5][%cal Bd2g5] } 3. Bf7#! { An amazing Boden's mate! } { [%csl Bh5,Yg5,Rh6,Rh4,Rg4,Bg6,Re5,Ra8][%cal Bf7h5,Yd2g5] } *


