39. Re7!! { Caruana sacrifices the rook! With the point of deflecting the queen from the e 8th rank. Almost every other move would have led to a draw. But this only works because of Caruana's follow up. } { [%csl Rc7][%cal Re7c7] } (39. Kb2?? { Any other move besides Re7 leads to a draw. } 39... Rg8 $10 { Covering the 8th rank again. There are no tactics here. }) 39... Qxe7 { If Black doesn't take the rook, White can play Rxc7+. } (39... Be8 { Prolongs the mate, covering c7. } { [%csl Rc7][%cal Rg7c7] } 40. Rxe8! { [%csl Ra8][%cal Rc6a8] } 40... Qxe8 41. Qxe8 { And checkmate will come from here. }) 40. Ba6!! { Another empty square sacrifice. Threatening Qb7#. } { [%csl Rb7][%cal Rc6b7] } 40... Kxa6 41. Qa8#! { Checkmate! } { [%csl Bb5,Rb6,Ra5,Ga6,Gb7,Ga7][%cal Ba4b5,Ga8a6,Ga8b7,Ga8a7] } *


