28... Rg1+ 29. Kf3 Qf1 30. Kf4!! Qxf2+ 31. Kg5!! Kg7 32. Rf4! Qxh2 33. Qf6+ Kh7 34. Qxg6+!! Kh8 35. Kh6! fxg6 36. Rxf8# *


[Event "Pure Brilliancy: Volume II: Persson vs Laurusas - Notes"]
[Date "2025.07.28"]
[White "Tiger Hillarp Persson"]
[Black "Tomas Laurusas"]
[Result "*"]
