2. d4 e5 { Our beloved Kennedy Variation. } 3. Nf3 { Nooo! White has forcefully transposed to the Scotch Game. We won't be able to play our usual stuff anymore. @Peng_Dehuai1898-1974 has created a great study explaining this variation in chapters 31-36: https://lichess.org/study/bZOUIzL2/QGRGbc9v } *


