1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5 3. Nc3 Qa5 4. d4 Nf6 5. Nf3 Bg4 6. h3 Qh5?? { black thinks the pawn cannot take the bishop because it is pinned } { but it can! } { [%csl Rh1,Gg4][%cal Rh5h1,Gh3g4] } 7. hxg4 Qxh1 { we now just have to reroute the Knight } { [%csl Bg3,Be2,Bh1][%cal Bc3e2,Be2g3,Bg3h1] } 8. Ne2 { black cannot do anything to save his queen. } { Black cannot prevent Ng3 } 8... Nxg4 (8... Ne4 { [%csl Gg3][%cal Ge4g3] } 9. Qd3 { [%cal Gd3e4] } 9... f5 10. gxf5 Nd6 11. Ng3) 9. Ng3 { The queen has no squares to go! } { [%csl Rh1,Rh5,Bh4,Bh2,Gh3,Bg1,Yh6,Gf1,Gg2][%cal Rg3h1,Rg3h5,Bf3h4,Bf3h2,Gg2h3,Bf3g1,Yc1h6,Ge1f1,Gf1g2] } *


