1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Nf6 3. d4 Nxd5 4. c4 Nb4 5. Qa4+ N8c6 6. a3 { +1 for White is nothing, practically it's "holdable" if White plays only-moves. } 6... Na6 7. d5 Nc5 8. Qb5?? { Natural, but losing for White because of the position of the queen } { [%csl Rc6,Re8][%cal Rb5e8,Rd5c6] } (8. Qc2? Nd4 9. Qd1 e5 10. Be3 (10. dxe6?? Bxe6 11. Be3 Ndb3 12. Qxd8+ Rxd8 13. Ra2 Bf5 14. Nc3 Nd3+ 15. Bxd3 Bxd3 { Black will not let White breathe }) 10... Bf5 11. Bxd4 exd4 { [%csl Gd4,Ga1][%cal Gd1d4,Gc5b3,Gb3d4,Gb3a1] } 12. b4 Qe7+ 13. Be2 $17 d3) 8... e5!! 9. dxc6 b6 { The queen is trapped! } { [%cal Ga7a6] } 10. Nf3 (10. Be3 a6 11. Bxc5 axb5 12. Bxf8 Rxf8 { queen vs 2 pieces }) 10... a6 { [%csl Gb4,Gb3,Ga4,Ga6,Gb6,Ga5,Gc5][%cal Rf8c5,Rc5b3,Ra6b5,Rb6a5,Rc5a4,Rc7b6,Ra8a6] } 11. Qb4 { [%csl Gb4,Ge1,Gd3][%cal Gc5d3,Gd3b4,Gd3e1,Gf8b4] } 11... Nd3+ $7 12. Bxd3 Bxb4+ 13. axb4 Qxd3 { [%csl Gf1][%cal Gd3f1] } *


