1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. f3 { [%csl Ge4][%cal Gf3e4] } 3... dxe4 4. fxe4 Nf6? { [%csl Ge4][%cal Gf6e4] } 5. e5 Nd5 6. c4 { [%csl Gd5][%cal Gc4d5] } 6... Nb6 7. Nc3 Bf5 8. Bd3 { offering a trade } { [%csl Gf5][%cal Gd3f5] } 8... Bxd3 (8... Qxd4 9. Bxf5 Qxe5+ 10. Be4 f5 11. Nf3 Qe6 12. Nd4 Qe5 13. O-O fxe4 14. Bf4 Qa5 15. Ne6 { [%csl Gc7][%cal Ge6c7] } 15... Na6 16. c5 Nxc5 17. Nc7+ Kf7 18. Be5+ Kg8 19. Qg4 g6 20. Qf4 { [%csl Gf7][%cal Gf4f7,Gf1f7] } 20... Qxa2 21. Rxa2 e3 22. Qf7#) 9. Qxd3 e6 10. Nf3 Be7 11. O-O O-O 12. Ne4 N8d7 13. Neg5 { threatening checkmate on h7 } { [%csl Gh7][%cal Gg5h7,Bd3h7] } 13... g6 (13... Bxg5 14. Nxg5 { [%csl Gh7][%cal Gg5h7,Gd3h7] } 14... g6 15. Qh3 h5 16. g4 { [%csl Gh5][%cal Gg4h5] }) 14. Qe4 Nxc4 15. Qh4 h5 16. g4 $18 { white will soon break open the kingside and checkmate } { [%csl Gh5][%cal Gg4h5] } *


