1... Na5?? 2. Bb5+ { [%csl Ge8][%cal Gb5e8] } 2... Bd7 3. Bxd7+ Kxd7 4. Qc2! { white's queen controls the c file and is planning to go to f5 } { [%csl Gc8,Gc7,Gc6,Gf5][%cal Gc2c8,Gc2f5] } 4... Rc8 { this is the most popular move. Our plan is simple, force the king away from the rook. } { [%csl Gc2][%cal Gc8c2] } (4... Nf6 5. Rxb7+! Nxb7 6. Qc6+ Kd8 7. Ne5 Nd6 (7... g6 8. Nxf7# { [%csl Gd8,Ye8,Yd7,Yc7,Yc8][%cal Gf7d8,Yc6e8,Yc6c8] }) (7... e6 8. Nxf7+ Ke7 9. Qxe6# { [%csl Ge8,Gd7,Ge7,Yd8,Be6,Gd6,Gf7,Rf8][%cal Ge6e8,Ge6d7,Yf7d8,Bd5e6,Ge6d6,Ge6f7] }) 8. Qxa8+ Kc7 { [%cal Gf1c1] } 9. O-O { [%csl Gc8,Gc7,Gc1][%cal Gc1c8,Gf1c1] } 9... Nb7 { [%csl Gb7][%cal Gb1b7] } 10. Rb1 Qa6 11. Rxb7+ Qxb7 12. Ba5+ Kd6 13. Nxf7+ Kc5 14. Qxb7) 5. Ne5+ { [%csl Gd7,Gf7][%cal Ge5d7,Ge5f7] } 5... Kd8 (5... Ke8 6. Qxc8#) 6. Nxf7+ Kd7 (6... Ke8 7. Qxc8+ Kxf7 8. Qe6+ Ke8 9. O-O { Rc1 Rc8 cannot be stopped } { [%csl Gc8,Gc1][%cal Gf1c1,Gc1c8] }) 7. Qf5+ Kc7 8. Bf4+ Qd6 9. Bxd6+ exd6 10. Rc1+ Kb6 11. Qxc8 Ne7 12. Rb1+ Ka6 13. Qc3 { white's queen wants to go to d3 } { [%csl Gd3,Ga6,Yb6,Yb5][%cal Gc3d3,Gd3a6,Yb1b6] } 13... b6 14. Nxd6 { [%csl Gb7,Gb5][%cal Gd6b7,Gd6b5] } 14... Nxd5 15. Qd3+ Nc4 16. Qxc4+ Ka5 17. Nb7# { [%csl Ga5,Ya4,Yb4,Yb5,Yc4,Ya6,Rb6][%cal Gb7a5,Yc4a4,Yc4a6] } *


