Qxe7+ Nxe7 (7... Kxe7 8. Bd3 Re8 9. O-O { white has a bishop for two pawns, the bishop pair, and a safe king. }) 8. Bxf6 gxf6 { [%csl Rb7,Rb4,Rd7,Rf7,Rf6,Rh7] }) 7. Bxf6 gxf6 { black's pawn structure is complete trash, and white has an extra piece on the board. } { [%csl Rb4,Rb7,Rd7,Rf7,Rf6,Rh7] } *


