1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. b4 Nxb4 4. c3 { [%csl Gb4][%cal Gc3b4] } 4... Nc6 5. d4 cxd4 6. cxd4 d5 7. exd5 Qxd5 8. Nc3 { [%csl Gd5][%cal Gc3d5] } 8... Qd8?? { now we can kick the knight away } 9. d5! { this is the only winning move } { [%csl Gc6][%cal Gd5c6] } 9... Nb8 10. Bb5+ { [%csl Ge8][%cal Gb5e8] } 10... Bd7 (10... Nd7 11. O-O a6 12. Bf4! axb5 13. Nxb5 { White is threatening to trap the queen with Bc7, or land a knight on c7 } { [%csl Bc7][%cal Gf4c7,Yb5c7] } 13... Qa5 14. Nc7+ Kd8 15. Rc1! Ra7 16. Ng5 { [%csl Gf7][%cal Gg5f7] } 16... Nh6 17. Nce6+ { [%csl Gd8,Bc7][%cal Ge6d8,Bf4c7,Yc1c7] } 17... fxe6 18. Bc7+ Qxc7 19. Nxe6+ Ke8 20. Nxc7+ Kf7 { even though material is more or less equal, white is just crushing here. } 21. Qb3 { [%csl Gf7][%cal Gb3f7] }) 11. O-O Nf6 (11... a6 12. Qa4 Nf6 13. Re1 g6 14. Ba3 Bxb5 15. Nxb5 Nbd7 16. Nd6# { [%csl Ge8,Re7,Bd8,Bf8,Bd7,Bf7][%cal Gd6e8,Ye1e8,Re7d6] }) 12. Re1 { white is now pinning the e7 pawn } { [%csl Ge8][%cal Ge1e8] } 12... g6? { This is the most popular move. Black is planning to fianchetto the dark squared bishop. White can now take advantage of the pin on e7. } (12... a6 13. Qa4 { [%csl Ga8,Rb5][%cal Ga4a8,Ra6b5] } 13... g6 14. Ba3 { [%csl Be7][%cal Ga3e7,Ye1e7] } 14... Bxb5 15. Nxb5 { white is threatening Nd6# } { [%csl Gd6][%cal Gb5d6] } 15... Nbd7 (15... axb5 16. Qxa8 Nxd5 17. Qxb7 e6 18. Bb2 { [%csl Gh8][%cal Gb2h8] } 18... Rg8) 16. Nd6# { a nice smothered mate! } { [%csl Re8,Be7,Rd6][%cal Ye1e8,Bd6e7,Gd6e8,Re7d6] }) 13. Ba3 { now black is unable to bring the bishop to g7. } { [%csl Be7][%cal Ga3e7,Ye1e7] } 13... a6 { [%csl Gb5][%cal Ga6b5] } (13... Qa5 14. Qb3 a6 15. Bf1 { [%csl Gb7][%cal Gb3b7] } 15... b5 16. Rad1 Qb6 17. Na4 { [%csl Gb6][%cal Ga4b6] } 17... Qa7 18. Qb2 $18 { [%csl Gf6][%cal Gb2f6] }) 14. Qd4! { we are counterattacking the knight. } { [%csl Gf6,Ye8,Re7][%cal Gd4f6,Re7f6,Ye1e8] } 14... axb5 15. Qxf6 { [%csl Gh8][%cal Gf6h8] } 15... Rxa3 { [%csl Gc3][%cal Ga3c3] } 16. Qxh8 Rxc3 { there is no need to take the rook, white can just go for checkmate. } { [%csl Gg5,Gh7,Gf8][%cal Gf3g5,Gg5h7,Gh7f8] } 17. Ng5 Rc5 18. Nxh7 { [%csl Bf8][%cal Gh7f8,Yh8f8] } 18... Bc8 (18... Be6 19. dxe6 { [%csl Gd7][%cal Ge6d7] } 19... fxe6 20. Qxf8+ Kd7 21. Rad1+ Rd5 22. Rxd5+ exd5 { black is gonna get mated very soon. }) 19. Nf6# { Smothered mate! } { [%csl Ge8,Gd7,Rf6][%cal Gf6e8,Gf6d7,Ye1e8,Re7f6] } *


