1. e4 e5 2. Nc3 Nc6 { The next 4 chapters will be about the Max Lange Defense } { The Max Lange Defense is when Black copies our move with 2...Nc6. It is a solid, flexible, & logical move and if Black plays perfectly they will get equality, that's the truth with most openings = perfect play will lead to equality, since chess played perfectly is always a draw. But our lines will score massive for us } *


