[ChapterName "crush 2...f5?"]
[ChapterURL "https://lichess.org/study/nq1GGbNO/RQ0aF0LP"]
[Annotator "https://lichess.org/@/Bosburp"]
[UTCDate "2023.09.25"]
[UTCTime "06:44:29"]

1. e4 e5 2. Nc3 f5? { a very dubious move, we can just take. in the Latvian gambit black gets some initiative with e4, kicking the knight away, but in the Vienna we don't have a knight on f3 :) } 3. exf5 Nf6 4. g4 { now we want to kick the knight away for Qh5+ } { [%csl Gf5,Gg5][%cal Gg4f5,Gg4g5] } 4... d5 (4... Bc5 5. g5 O-O 6. gxf6 Qxf6 7. Qf3 d6 8. Ne4 { we just want to trade material, because we are up a knight. } 8... Qxf5 9. Qxf5 Bxf5 10. Nxc5 dxc5) (4... h6 5. Nf3 Nxg4 6. Rg1 Nf6 7. d4 e4 8. Ne5 { [%csl Gg6][%cal Ge5g6] } 8... d5 9. Nxd5 Qxd5 10. Bc4 Qd6 11. Bf7+ Ke7) 5. g5 Ne4 (5... d4 6. gxf6 dxc3 7. Qh5+ { [%csl Ge8][%cal Gh5e8] } 7... Kd7 8. Qf7+ Kc6 9. Bg2+ { [%csl Gc6][%cal Gg2b7] } 9... e4 10. Qc4+ Kd7 (10... Kd6 11. Qd4+ Kc6 12. Bxe4+ Kb5 13. a4+ Ka5 14. Qxd8) 11. Qe6#) 6. Qh5+ { [%csl Ge8,Yg6][%cal Gh5e8,Yf5g6] } 6... Ke7 (6... g6 7. fxg6 hxg6 8. Qxh8) 7. f6+ gxf6 8. d4 Qe8 (8... Nxc3 9. gxf6+ Kxf6 10. Bg5+ { [%csl Gd8,Gf6][%cal Gg5d8] } 10... Ke6 11. Bxd8 $18) 9. Nxd5+ Kd8 10. Qxe8+ Kxe8 11. Nxc7+ { [%csl Ge8,Ga8][%cal Gc7e8,Gc7a8] } 11... Kd8 12. Nxa8 $18 *


