1. e4 { here's a fun game I came across. NOTE: this was a blitz game. } 1... e5 2. Nc3 Nc6 3. f4?! { Inaccuracy. Bc4 was best. } (3. Bc4 Nf6 4. d3 Bb4 5. Nf3 d6 6. O-O Na5 7. Bb5+ c6) 3... exf4 4. Nf3 g5 5. Bc4? { Mistake. g3 was best. } (5. g3 Bg7 6. d4 d6 7. d5 Ne5 8. gxf4 gxf4 9. Bxf4 Bg4) 5... g4 6. O-O gxf3 7. Bxf7+?? { Blunder. Qxf3 was best. } { that's maybe a bit much :D } (7. Qxf3 Bc5+ 8. Kh1 Qh4 9. d4 Nxd4 10. Qd3 f3 11. g3 Qh3) 7... Kxf7 8. Qxf3 Bh6? { Mistake. Qg5 was best. } (8... Qg5 9. d4) 9. d4 Nxd4?? { Blunder. Qf6 was best. } (9... Qf6 10. Bxf4 Bxf4 11. Nd5 Qxd4+ 12. Rf2 Qe5 13. Nxf4 Nd4 14. Qa3 Nf6 15. Raf1 Nb5 16. Qd3) 10. Qh5+ { [%csl Gf7][%cal Gh5f7] } 10... Kg7 11. Bxf4 d6 12. Be5+!! { 1-0 Black resigns. } { a killer blow } { [%csl Gf7][%cal Yf1f7,Bh5f7] } 1-0


