1. e4 Nf6 2. Nc3 d5 3. exd5 Nxd5 4. Nge2 Nc6 5. g3? { white wants to fianchetto his bishop and castle } { [%csl Gg2][%cal Gf1g2] } 5... Bg4 { black pins the knight } { [%csl Gd1,Ge2][%cal Gg4d1] } 6. Bg2 Nd4! { we sacrifice our knight! } { [%csl Gd5,Gd4][%cal Gg2d5,Gc3d5,Ge2d4] } 7. Bxd5 Qxd5! 8. Nxd5 { White is up a full queen, but black has a mate is 2! } (8. f3 Nxf3+ 9. Kf2 Qf5 10. d3 Ng5+ 11. Ke1 Nf3+ 12. Kf2 $19) 8... Nf3+ 9. Kf1 Bh3# { Checkmate! } { [%csl Gf1,Bg1,Be1,Gg2,Ye2,Rf2][%cal Gh3f1,Bf3g1,Bf3e1] } *


