1. e4 Nf6 2. e5 Nd5 3. d4 d6 4. Nf3 dxe5 5. Nxe5 c6 6. c4?! Nb4 7. a3 Qxd4! 8. Qxd4 { [%cal Gc2e1] } (8. axb4 Qxe5+ { black still has a slight advantage }) (8. Nxf7 Qe4+ 9. Be2 Nc2+ 10. Kf1 Nxa1 11. Nxh8 Bf5 12. Nc3 Qc2 13. g4 Qxd1+ 14. Bxd1 Bd3+ 15. Be2 Bxe2+ 16. Nxe2 Nb3 $15 { black is slightly better. white's knight is trapped, while black doesn't really have any problems. }) 8... Nc2+ { [%csl Ge1,Gd4][%cal Gc2d4,Gc2e1] } 9. Kd1 Nxd4 { Black has a 3.3 advantage } *


