[UTCTime "08:48:44"]
[ChapterMode "gamebook"]

{ Hello, welcome to this study!

I will be showing you some traps in the Kings Gambit (for white and black).

In this chapter I will be showing you what the Kings Gambit is.
Start by playing e4 :) }
1. e4 e5 2. f4 { Yes, this is the King's Gambit!
The King's Gambit is one of the oldest documented openings, The main idea for white is to develop his pieces quickly, and to control the center.
Black has 2 options here, to accept the gambit or to decline it
You can read more about the King's Gambit here: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/King%27s_Gambit } *


