1. e4 e5 2. f4 exf4 3. Nf3 { [%csl Gh4][%cal Gf3h4,Rd8h4,Rh4e1] } 3... g5 { [%csl Gf4,Gg4][%cal Gg5f4,Gg5g4] } 4. Bc4 h6 { [%csl Gg5,Gf4,Gh6][%cal Gh6g5,Gg5f4] } 5. h4 { [%csl Gg5][%cal Gh4g5] } 5... f6?? { black doesn't want to ruin his lovely pawn chain } { [%csl Gg5][%cal Gh4g5,Gf6g5] } 6. Ne5 { a killer move! } { [%csl Gf7,Gh5][%cal Ge5f7,Gc4f7,Gd1h5,Gh5f7] } 6... fxe5 (6... h5 7. Bf7+ Ke7 8. Ng6+ Kxf7 9. Nxh8+ Kg7 10. Qxh5 g4 11. Ng6 { you still have a great position }) (6... d5 7. Qh5+ Ke7 8. Qf7+ Kd6 9. Qxd5+ Ke7 10. Ng6+ Ke8 11. Qf7#) 7. Qh5+ Ke7 8. Qf7+ Kd6 9. Qd5+ Ke7 10. Qxe5# *


