1. e4 { I got this trap from @WassimBerbar, he makes great studies! Go check them out here: https://lichess.org/study/by/WassimBerbar } 1... e5 2. f4 exf4 3. Nf3 g5 { [%csl Rg4,Rf4][%cal Rg5g4,Rg5f4] } 4. h4 { [%csl Gg5][%cal Gh4g5] } 4... g4 { [%csl Rf3][%cal Rg4f3] } 5. Ne5 { [%csl Gg4][%cal Ge5g4] } 5... Nf6 6. Nxg4 Nxe4 7. d3 { [%csl Ge4][%cal Gd3e4] } 7... Ng3 { [%csl Rh1][%cal Rg3h1] } 8. Bxf4! Qe7+ 9. Be2 Nxh1?? 10. Bg5!! { black's queen can only go on the blue squares } { [%csl Ge7,Re5,Re4,Re3,Rf6,Rd8,Bb4,Bc5,Bd6,Ra3,Be6][%cal Gg5e7] } 10... Qe6? (10... Nc6 11. Bxe7 (11. Nf6+ Kd8 12. Nd5 f6 13. Bxf6 Qxf6 14. Nxf6)) (10... Qd6 11. Nf6+ Kd8 12. Ne4+ { [%csl Gd6,Gd8][%cal Ge4d6,Gg5d8] }) (10... Qc5 11. Nf6+ Kd8 12. Ne4+ { [%csl Gc5][%cal Ge4c5] }) (10... Qb4+ 11. c3 Qxb2 12. Nf6+ Kd8 (12... Ke7) 13. Nd5+ Ke8 (13... Be7 14. Bxe7+ Ke8 15. Ba3 { [%csl Gb2,Gc7][%cal Ga3b2,Gd5c7] } 15... Qxa1 16. Bh5 Qxb1 (16... Ng3 17. Bxf7+ Kxf7 18. Qf3+ Ke8 19. Qe3+ Kf7 20. Qe7+ { [%csl Gg8,Gf8][%cal Gf7g8,Ge7f8] } 20... Kg6 21. Qf6+ Kh5 22. Qg5#)) 14. Nxc7#) (10... f6 11. Nxf6+ Kf7) 11. Nf6+ { [%csl Ge8][%cal Gf6e8] } 11... Kd8 12. Nd5+ { [%csl Gd8][%cal Gg5d8] } 12... f6 (12... Be7 13. Bxe7+ Ke8 14. Nxc7+ Kxe7 15. Nxe6) (12... Ke8 13. Nxc7# { mate! } { [%csl Ge8,Ge6,Bd8,Be7,Bf6][%cal Gc7e8,Gc7e6,Bg5d8] }) 13. Bxf6+ Be7 14. Bxe7+ Ke8 15. Nxc7+ { [%csl Ge8,Ge6][%cal Gc7e8,Gc7e6] } 15... Kxe7 16. Nxe6 dxe6 { white has a +9.8 advantage! } { [%csl Re7,Rh1] } *


