1. e4 e5 2. f4 d5 { this is called Falkbeer CG (Counter Gambit) } 3. exd5 c6 4. Qe2 { white pins the pawn } { [%csl Re8][%cal Re2e8] } 4... cxd5 5. Qxe5+?! Be7! 6. Qxg7?? { white thinks he is completely winning but he missed something } { [%csl Gh8][%cal Gg7h8] } 6... Bf6 { [%csl Gg7,Gh8,Rg6,Bh6,Gg5,Yg4][%cal Gf6g7,Gg7h8,Rf7g6,Bg8h6,Gf6g5,Yc8g4] } 7. Qg3 { this is blacks only safe move } 7... Bh4 { the queen is lost } { [%csl Ge1,Gg3][%cal Gh4e1] } 8. Nc3 Bxg3+ 9. hxg3 *


