1. e4 e5 2. f4 d5 3. Nf3 { [%csl Gh4][%cal Gf3h4] } 3... dxe4 { [%csl Gf3][%cal Ge4f3] } 4. Nxe5 Nc6 { [%csl Ge5][%cal Gc6e5] } 5. Bb5 { the knight is pinned } { [%csl Ge8][%cal Gb5e8] } 5... Nf6 { amazing! black sacs his rook } 6. Nxc6 { [%csl Gd8][%cal Gc6d8] } 6... bxc6 7. Bxc6+ { [%csl Ge8,Ga8][%cal Gc6e8,Gc6a8] } 7... Bd7 8. Bxa8? Bg4 { BOOM! white cannot do anything to save his queen, black has a 3.2 advantage here } { [%csl Gd1][%cal Gg4d1] } *


