{ This is the Spanish version of the Fishing pole trap }
1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Bxc6 dxc6 5. O-O Bg4 { [%csl Gd1,Gf3][%cal Gg4d1] } 6. h3 h5 7. hxg4? hxg4 8. Nxe5?? Qh4 { white cannot stop mate! } { [%csl Gh2,Gh1][%cal Gh4h2,Gh2h1] } 9. f4 g3 10. Qh5 Rxh5 11. a3 Qh2# { here is a similar game: https://lichess.org/q7kvXTuI/black#20 } *


