1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. d3 { [%csl Gg5,Ge3][%cal Gc1g5] } 4... Ne7! 5. Nxe5? { white will lose his knight or his bishop! } 5... c6 { Stockfish recommends white to sack his knight on f7 lol } { [%csl Gb5,Ga5][%cal Gc6b5,Gd8a5] } 6. Nc4 { [%csl Rd6][%cal Rc4d6] } (6. Ba4 Qa5+ { [%csl Ga4,Ge5][%cal Ga5a4,Ga5e5] } 7. Nc3 Qxe5) 6... Ng6 (6... cxb5 7. Nd6# { Watch out for this! }) 7. Ba4 { this is the only "safe" square for white. } 7... b5 { [%csl Gc4,Ga4][%cal Gb5c4,Gb5a4] } *


